1327
01:21:57.847 --> 01:21:59.808
Charlie. you won't believe this.

1328
01:21:59.891 --> 01:22:01.935
He's brought in
three armored trucks.

1329
01:22:02.018 --> 01:22:05.564
It's a shell game.
Shell game now.

1330
01:22:05.648 --> 01:22:07.399
Well. boss.
I can't reroute the truck

1331
